Generate the HTML code for a landing page based on this structure:

Page Title: {{ structure.title }}
Description: {{ structure.description }}

Color Scheme:
- Primary: {{ structure.color_scheme.primary }}
- Secondary: {{ structure.color_scheme.secondary }}
- Accent: {{ structure.color_scheme.accent }}
- Text: {{ structure.color_scheme.text }}
- Background: {{ structure.color_scheme.background }}

Header:
- Logo: {{ structure.header.logo }}
- Navigation Items:
{%- for item in structure.header.navigation %}
  - {{ item.text }} ({% if item.is_button %}Button{% else %}Link{% endif %})
{%- endfor %}
- Sticky: {{ structure.header.is_sticky }}
- Mobile Menu: {{ structure.header.has_mobile_menu }}

Hero Section:
- Title: {{ structure.hero.title }}
- Subtitle: {{ structure.hero.subtitle }}
- Primary CTA: {{ structure.hero.cta_primary.text }}
{%- if structure.hero.cta_secondary %}
- Secondary CTA: {{ structure.hero.cta_secondary.text }}
{%- endif %}
- Background: {{ structure.hero.background_type }} ({{ structure.hero.background_content }})

Features Section:
- Title: {{ structure.features.title }}
- Subtitle: {{ structure.features.subtitle }}
- Layout: {{ structure.features.layout }}
- Features:
{%- for feature in structure.features.features %}
  - {{ feature.title }}: {{ feature.description }}
{%- endfor %}

Testimonials Section:
- Title: {{ structure.testimonials.title }}
- Subtitle: {{ structure.testimonials.subtitle }}
- Testimonials:
{%- for testimonial in structure.testimonials.testimonials %}
  - {{ testimonial.quote }} - {{ testimonial.author }}, {{ testimonial.role }} at {{ testimonial.company }}
{%- endfor %}

CTA Section:
- Title: {{ structure.cta.title }}
- Subtitle: {{ structure.cta.subtitle }}
- Button: {{ structure.cta.button.text }}
- Style: {{ structure.cta.background_style }}

Footer:
- Logo: {{ structure.footer.logo }}
- Description: {{ structure.footer.description }}
- Social Links:
{%- for link in structure.footer.social_links %}
  - {{ link.text }}: {{ link.link }}
{%- endfor %}

Requirements:
1. Use semantic HTML5 elements
2. Include Tailwind CSS classes
3. Make it fully responsive
4. Add proper ARIA attributes
5. Include comments for each major section
6. Use proper meta tags
7. Add loading attributes for images/videos
8. Include viewport settings
